    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Today we are doing nothing. We wake up at 6am to the sound of a goat strapped to the back of the motorcycle screaming its lungs out. We manage to sleep to 8:30am. The budget is real today - but luckily breakfast is included. We both have a full english breakfast and then scavenge quite a few plates of food and plungers of coffee that guests have left unfinished.",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
